SUMMARY:Ride to Paris-Roubaix Watch Party
DESCRIPTION:Lancaster Bicycle Club (LBC) Meetup\nThis is a leisurely ride 
 from Landis Valley Museum to the Common Wheel on East King St in Lancaster
  City to join the Paris-Roubaix Watch Party. We will leave Landis Valley a
 t 8 am and will take less traveled roads to the venue.
