SUMMARY:Competitive Ride (A+) - CV Throttles and Bottles (43H)
DESCRIPTION:Lancaster Bicycle Club (LBC) Meetup\nAnticipated average pace:
  **20+ mph**\n\nCue and GPX link:[https://ridewithgps.com/routes/30097204]
 (https://ridewithgps.com/routes/30097204)\n\n**This ride is intended for t
 he experienced group rider in good physical condition and capable of maint
 aining a steady pace. Few stops if any. Riders unable to maintain the pace
  may be dropped. If unsure if this ride is for you\, it is recommended you
  try the "A" ride option first.**\n\nHelmets are mandatory. No earbuds. Pl
 ease bring water and a basic repair kit (spare tube\, tire levers\, pump/C
 O2 inflator).\n\nTo eliminate passing around a pen and paper waiver\, we r
 equire an LBC Club membership and Meetup RSVP below to join this ride.\n\n
 Being on Meetup does not mean you are a club member. [Join here](https://w
 ww.lancasterbikeclub.net/content.aspx?page_id=60&club_id=257148).\n\nYour 
 RSVP is your agreement to abide by the club's [Code of Conduct](https://la
 ncbikeclub.clubexpress.com/content.aspx?page_id=22&club_id=257148&module_i
 d=323984)\,\n\n[Rules of the Road](https://lancbikeclub.clubexpress.com/co
 ntent.aspx?page_id=22&club_id=257148&module_id=325159)
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/lancaster-bicycle-club/events/3142322
 76/
