SUMMARY:Casual Ride (D) -WH Udder Choice Sundae Ride (20R)
DESCRIPTION:Lancaster Bicycle Club (LBC) Meetup\nRide leader: Judy Wells\n
 Sweep: Jen Weese\nCue and GPX link: [Udder Choice Sundae Ride](https://rou
 tes.lancasterbikeclub.net/cue/wh-udder-choice-sundae-ride-20r-2/)\n\nThis 
 is a Casual (D) level group ride with an average of pace 12-14 mph. The in
 tent of this and all LBC rides is to be safe\, have fun\, stay together.\n
 \nHelmets are mandatory. No earbuds. Please bring water and a basic repair
  kit (spare tube\, tire levers\, pump/CO2 inflator).\n\nWe require LBC Clu
 b membership and Meetup RSVP to join this ride.\nBeing on Meetup does not 
 mean you are a club member.[Join the Club](https://www.lancasterbikeclub.n
 et/content.aspx?page_id=60&club_id=257148)\n\nYour RSVP is your agreement 
 to abide by the club's:\n[Code of Conduct](https://lancbikeclub.clubexpres
 s.com/content.aspx?page_id=22&club_id=257148&module_id=323984)\n[Rules of 
 the Road](https://lancbikeclub.clubexpress.com/content.aspx?page_id=22&clu
 b_id=257148&module_id=325159)\n[Ride Waiver](https://lancasterbikeclub.net
 /docs.ashx?id=763523)
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/lancaster-bicycle-club/events/3134749
 55/
