SUMMARY:Intermediate Ride (C) - DH Donegal Delight (28R)
DESCRIPTION:Lancaster Bicycle Club (LBC) Meetup\n**Be Safe\, Have Fun\, an
 d Ride Together**\n\nRide leader: Garen Evans\nAnticipated Average Pace: (
 14-16 mph)\nRoute: [https://routes.lancasterbikeclub.net/cue/dh-donegal-de
 light-28r/](https://routes.lancasterbikeclub.net/cue/dh-donegal-delight-28
 r/)\n\nThis is an Intermediate C Class ride. The ride leader will ride at 
 the advertised average speed. This is intended to be a group ride with a n
 o-drop rule as the main goal. The ride leader will do his/her best to keep
  the group together with occasional regroupings and/or splitting into mult
 iple groups to align to pace capabilities.\n\nPlease do not join this ride
  if you are not willing to ride with the group. If you exceed the posted p
 ace\, you will be riding by yourself and encouraged to join a faster group
 . If maintaining a 14-16 mph average is beyond your current ability level\
 , please consider joining a slower ride first.\n\nHelmets are mandatory. N
 o earbuds. Please bring water and a basic repair kit (spare tube\, tire le
 vers\, pump/CO2 inflator).\n\nTo eliminate passing around a pen and paper 
 waiver\, we require LBC Club membership and Meetup RSVP below to join this
  ride. Being on Meetup does not mean you are a club member. Join here [Mem
 ber Signup](https://www.lancasterbikeclub.net/content.aspx?page_id=60&club
 _id=257148)\n\nYour RSVP is your agreement to abide by the club's Code of 
 Conduct: [Code of Conduct](https://www.lancasterbikeclub.net/content.aspx?
 page_id=22&club_id=257148&module_id=323984)\n\nGuidance if an incident occ
 urs: [Incident Actions](https://lancasterbikeclub.net/content.aspx?page_id
 =22&club_id=257148&module_id=326137)
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/lancaster-bicycle-club/events/3141535
 12/
